---
title: Sesame-Crusted Tuna Tataki Salad with Rice Balls, Avocado, and Wasabi-Lime Dressing
description: Tataki refers to the cooking method of quickly searing over high heat. This allows the tuna to have a crunchy sesame crust with a beautifully rare center. Rolling rice into balls is a fun step for the whole family—be sure to grab a helper!
